
Rules:

The goal of the game is to guess the unique 4 digit number.

Each guess has to be 4 digits with no repeated numbers

The matching digits in the right position are "Bulls"
The matching digits in different positions are "Cows"

Log in with user name to save High Score based on fastest time

During the game, type "answer" or "a" to quit the current game and see the answer
Type "quit" or "q" to quit the game and to go back to Main Menu

Bulls = correct code, correct position.
Cows = correct code, wrong position.


